      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Defense in depth: each layer is independent. A bug that breaks Layer 1 still has Layers 2 and 3 preventing cross-tenant data access.\nLayer 3 (RLS) is the last line of defense — it operates below the application and cannot be bypassed by application bugs.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "footer-box",
      "originalText": "Defense in depth: each layer is independent. A bug that breaks Layer 1 still has Layers 2 and 3 preventing cross-tenant data access.\nLayer 3 (RLS) is the last line of defense — it operates below the application and cannot be bypassed by application bugs.",
